  "description": "A TRUE OASIS OF FIVE-STAR LEISURE & WELLNESS EXPERIENCES AT THE BEACHFRONT!\nBeing one of the most granted hotels on the island, Rodos Palladium has earned a reputation for pleasing even the most demanding holidaymakers. This 5-star premier-class resort occupies a prominent position on the Blue Flag-awarded sandy & pebble beach of Kallithea. The establishment is renowned for its genuine, timeless passion for providing Greek hospitality, offering its guests an authentic experience with meticulous attention to detail. Fine Greek & Mediterranean tastes, cosmopolitan bars, a large tropical pool and a Spa with an indoor heated pool mark Rodos Palladium the ideal choice for your stay in Rhodes. Situated within just 8 km distance from Rhodes town, it unquestionably guarantees a relaxing and carefree holiday environment.\nDress Code: The following attire is NOT ACCEPTED: Sports shorts or training trousers, sports t-shirts or tank tops or sleeveless shirts and flip-flops.",
